title: DDFP 204: Jordan Cameron & Weekend Guide
itunes:title: DDFP 204: Jordan Cameron & Weekend Guide
description:
In a special edition of the #DDFP, Shek hosts the new video segment "NFL.com's Weekend Guide" with Akbar Gbajabiamila, Adam Rank and Dan Hanzus to break down Cam Newton and Colin Kaepernick on and off the football field and much more. Adam Rank then interviews Cleveland Browns tight end Jordan Cameron discussing everything from superheroes to movies.
